  "title": "Technical Sales Engineer (Power Supply Application)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Provide technical sales support to both local and overseas markets.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with customers on product development, customization, and modification needs.</li>\n  <li>Conduct technical training and presentations on product applications.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with the sales and marketing teams to achieve business and sales objectives.</li>\n  <li>Offer post-sales technical assistance and ensure customer satisfaction.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree or Diploma in Electrical/Electronics Engineering or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>At least 4 years of relevant experience in <strong>power supply, electronics, or industrial equipment.</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong technical understanding of <strong>power supply products and applications.</strong></li>\n  <li>Good communication and presentation skills to engage with customers and internal teams.</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated, independent, and results-driven individual.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701<br>\nRegistration: R21100996</p>",
